  {
    "model": "Qwen3.6-27B",
    "run": 5,
    "chapter_id": "C2",
    "quest_data": {
      "chapter_id": "C2",
      "chapter_title": "The Puppeteer's Strings",
      "quest_type": "main",
      "required": true,
      "scale": "large",
      "quests": [
        {
          "quest_id": "Q2_1",
          "quest_title": "Whispers in the Village",
          "steps": [
            {
              "step": 1,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "dock",
                "to": "village"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 2,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "village",
                "to": "store"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 3,
              "action": "TALK",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "target": "anne",
                "place": "store",
                "dialogue_content": [
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "Anne, I'm looking for answers. People are saying there's someone pulling the strings behind all this."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "anne",
                    "line": "Pulling strings? That's a poetic way to describe a tyrant. Viktor has been consolidating power in the Outpost. He controls who gets resources and who doesn't."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "Is that all he's doing? It feels like there's more to it."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "anne",
                    "line": "There is. He's working with The Doctor. They're running experiments in the deep levels of the Outpost. But you can't just walk in there. You'll need the outpost key."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "Where can I find one?"
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "anne",
                    "line": "I don't have one. But George at the powerstation might know who does, or he might have seen something useful. Check with him."
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "quest_id": "Q2_2",
          "quest_title": "Power to the People",
          "steps": [
            {
              "step": 4,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "store",
                "to": "village"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 5,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "village",
                "to": "powerstation"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 6,
              "action": "TALK",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "target": "george",
                "place": "powerstation",
                "dialogue_content": [
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "George, Anne sent me. I need to get into the Outpost to stop Viktor and The Doctor. Do you have the key?"
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "george",
                    "line": "No. I keep the lights on. I don't play guard dog. But I know the layout. The main entrance is locked, yes. But there's a service route through the graveyard."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "The graveyard? Is it safe?"
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "george",
                    "line": "Safer than the front door. It connects to the lower levels. You'll need to be quiet. And if you see The Doctor... don't trust his science. It's built on bodies."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "Thanks, George. I'll keep that in mind."
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "quest_id": "Q2_3",
          "quest_title": "Into the Lion's Den",
          "steps": [
            {
              "step": 7,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "powerstation",
                "to": "village"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 8,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "village",
                "to": "graveyard"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 9,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "graveyard",
                "to": "outpost1"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 10,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "outpost1",
                "to": "outpost2"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 11,
              "action": "TALK",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "target": "viktor",
                "place": "outpost2",
                "dialogue_content": [
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "Viktor. You're the one pulling the strings."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "viktor",
                    "line": "Strings? I provide order. Without me, this island is chaos. The Doctor provides the means to control the infected. It is a necessary alliance."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "It's not an alliance. It's exploitation. You're using people as test subjects."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "viktor",
                    "line": "Progress requires sacrifice. Go ahead, tell the villagers. They will thank me when they are safe in my walls. Or you can try to stop me. I doubt you'll succeed."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "I'm not here to debate you. I'm here to end it."
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "quest_id": "Q2_4",
          "quest_title": "The Source of the Plague",
          "steps": [
            {
              "step": 12,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "outpost2",
                "to": "outpost3"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 13,
              "action": "TALK",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "target": "the_doctor",
                "place": "outpost3",
                "dialogue_content": [
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "The Doctor. Viktor says you're helping him. What are you really doing here?"
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "the_doctor",
                    "line": "I am refining the pathogen. Viktor is merely a... logistical necessity. He keeps the variables contained so I can observe the results."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "You're creating this? You're the one behind the outbreak?"
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "the_doctor",
                    "line": "I am accelerating evolution. The current state of humanity is inefficient. My work will ensure only the strong survive. Viktor ensures I am not interrupted."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "You're a monster. This ends today."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "the_doctor",
                    "line": "You cannot stop science. But you can certainly try. I suggest you focus on your own survival. The experiment is not yet complete."
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "quest_id": "Q2_5",
          "quest_title": "Exposing the Truth",
          "steps": [
            {
              "step": 14,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "outpost3",
                "to": "outpost2"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 15,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "outpost2",
                "to": "outpost1"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 16,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "outpost1",
                "to": "graveyard"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 17,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "graveyard",
                "to": "village"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 18,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "village",
                "to": "store"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 19,
              "action": "TALK",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "target": "anne",
                "place": "store",
                "dialogue_content": [
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "Anne, I found the truth. The Doctor created the pathogen. Viktor is helping him contain it to protect his research."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "anne",
                    "line": "I suspected as much. The Doctor is a madman, and Viktor is a butcher. If this gets out, the village will turn on them."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "We need to make sure everyone knows. Can you spread the word?"
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "anne",
                    "line": "I have my network. I'll make sure the right people hear this. But be careful. Viktor won't take this lying down. He'll come for you."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "Let him try. I'm ready."
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "model": "Qwen3.6-27B",
    "run": 5,
    "chapter_id": "C3",
    "quest_data": {
      "chapter_id": "C3",
      "chapter_title": "The Last Horizon",
      "quest_type": "main",
      "required": true,
      "scale": "large",
      "quests": [
        {
          "quest_id": "Q3_01",
          "quest_title": "Departure",
          "steps": [
            {
              "step": 1,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "store",
                "to": "village"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 2,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "village",
                "to": "dock"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 3,
              "action": "TALK",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "target": "mary",
                "place": "dock",
                "dialogue_content": [
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "Mary, the boat is fixed. Is it ready to go?"
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "mary",
                    "line": "She's running. Engine's hot, fuel's full. I've been waiting for this moment since the outbreak started."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "We're leaving. Right now. The island isn't safe, and neither are we."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "mary",
                    "line": "Then get on board. We don't have much time before the sun goes down and the horde moves."
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 4,
              "action": "TALK",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "target": "mary",
                "place": "dock",
                "dialogue_content": [
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "This is it. We're getting off this rock."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "mary",
                    "line": "Yeah. It's a new start. Or at least, a chance at one."
                  },
                  {
